1
00:01:03,710 --> 00:01:05,910
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,260 --> 00:01:09,890
[Episode 6]

3
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,509
Xie Jiuzhao?

4
00:01:37,229 --> 00:01:41,280
[Last night]

5
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,120
You're drunk.

6
00:02:00,950 --> 00:02:02,400
I'm not drunk.

7
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,430
What are you afraid of?

8
00:02:06,430 --> 00:02:09,190
Have I gone mad?

9
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:29,750
You think you can just walk away

10
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:31,310
like nothing happened?

11
00:02:31,310 --> 00:02:31,870
You...

12
00:02:36,870 --> 00:02:38,910
What does Your Majesty want?

13
00:02:39,030 --> 00:02:41,960
Since I've offended you,
I'll accept my punishment.

14
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:47,060
Did you sleep well last night?

15
00:02:49,170 --> 00:02:50,440
I'm not drunk.

16
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:51,740
What are you afraid of?

17
00:02:57,079 --> 00:03:00,680
Do you really think I'm afraid of you?

18
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:01,610
Where...

19
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,470
Where am I?

20
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,190
My bedchamber.

21
00:04:09,590 --> 00:04:11,910
I was drunk last night
and offended Your Majesty.

22
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:13,470
Since Your Majesty is so generous

23
00:04:13,470 --> 00:04:14,750
and hasn't held it against me,

24
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:16,720
I'll take my leave now.

25
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,560
Stop!

26
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,570
You're not going anywhere.

27
00:04:22,070 --> 00:04:22,510
You...

28
00:04:22,510 --> 00:04:24,240
If you're worried about your maid,

29
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:26,920
I've sent people to protect her.
You can rest easy.

30
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,480
Report!

31
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:30,280
Your Majesty, I have
urgent matters to report.

32
00:04:32,270 --> 00:04:34,720
If you need anything,
just ask someone to arrange it.

33
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:37,050
We'll discuss everything after I return.

34
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,750
By my order,

35
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,950
Miss Jiang is not allowed
to leave the imperial chamber.

36
00:04:42,950 --> 00:04:44,010
Yes, Your Majesty.

37
00:04:51,270 --> 00:04:51,870
Speak.

38
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:54,480
The assassin who escaped
from Chunliu Garden has been caught

39
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,540
and is now imprisoned in the dungeon.

40
00:04:58,510 --> 00:05:00,040
I will interrogate him myself.

41
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,100
Yes, Your Majesty.

42
00:05:01,190 --> 00:05:02,000
Jiuzhao.

43
00:05:02,510 --> 00:05:03,270
Nianzhao.

44
00:05:03,870 --> 00:05:04,950
I'll take my leave.

45
00:05:06,310 --> 00:05:07,970
Where are you going, Jiuzhao?

46
00:05:09,190 --> 00:05:09,800
What?

47
00:05:10,070 --> 00:05:12,830
Do I need to report
my whereabouts to you now?

48
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:16,360
I've overstepped my bounds.

49
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:18,190
Today, the scholars at the Hanlin Academy

50
00:05:18,190 --> 00:05:19,480
praised my writing,

51
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:21,720
but compared to yours in the past,

52
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,980
mine is still lacking.

53
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,630
I came today

54
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:26,560
hoping you could review it.

55
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:29,340
Your literary skills
have long surpassed mine.

56
00:05:29,870 --> 00:05:32,120
Having the Hanlin scholars
teach you is sufficient.

57
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:34,240
I have matters to attend to today.

58
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:37,800
I'll follow your instruction.

59
00:05:38,390 --> 00:05:41,430
About last night, you...

60
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,750
I'm just curious.

61
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:50,440
I intended to take a walk
with you last night

62
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:52,560
but couldn't find you anywhere.

63
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:55,310
I was tired and retired early.

64
00:05:55,950 --> 00:05:56,830
Nianzhao,

65
00:05:57,510 --> 00:05:58,750
anything else?

66
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,360
While state affairs are demanding,

67
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:03,510
please take care of your health.

68
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:06,360
Farewell.

69
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,750
I know you're a sworn warrior,

70
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,070
but

71
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,830
as long as you're not dead,

72
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:41,920
I have plenty of ways to get you to speak.

73
00:06:56,190 --> 00:06:58,159
Quite the tough one.

74
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,070
These rats

75
00:07:04,510 --> 00:07:06,560
have been starving for over 3 weeks.

76
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,510
In a moment,

77
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:10,720
I'll have you coated in honey syrup,

78
00:07:10,870 --> 00:07:14,070
so they can have a proper feast.

79
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,290
Don't worry,

80
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,920
I'll leave your head intact

81
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:20,630
so you can watch yourself being devoured

82
00:07:20,630 --> 00:07:23,360
and die a spectacular death.

83
00:07:32,390 --> 00:07:33,240
It was the Empress Dowager!

84
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:35,770
It was the Empress Dowager
who gave the order!

85
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:40,120
The Empress Dowager
ordered you to kill me?

86
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:42,360
To kill... To kill Miss Jiang.

87
00:07:42,430 --> 00:07:44,480
Her Majesty ordered us to spare no expense

88
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:46,270
to take Miss Jiang's life.

89
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,720
If the Empress Dowager
wanted to kill Miss Jiang,

90
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,310
then why

91
00:08:02,310 --> 00:08:04,510
would she arrange
her marriage to General Xun?

92
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:07,310
She's always treated General Xun
far more favorably than she treats you.

93
00:08:07,310 --> 00:08:08,160
How could...

94
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,240
Speak.

95
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:22,360
Where has Jiang Li gone?

96
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:25,040
General, I truly don't know.

97
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,870
I wouldn't dare lie to you.

98
00:08:27,870 --> 00:08:30,630
Jiang Li came alone last night.

99
00:08:30,630 --> 00:08:32,270
And then, strangely enough,

100
00:08:32,270 --> 00:08:33,549
a young gentleman arrived

101
00:08:33,549 --> 00:08:34,840
with many followers,

102
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:37,120
and asked everyone here to leave,

103
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:39,320
saying he wanted
to reserve the entire theater.

104
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:41,909
I don't know what happened after that.

105
00:08:43,909 --> 00:08:45,550
What did that man look like?

106
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:47,550
The man's about six feet tall,

107
00:08:47,870 --> 00:08:49,320
with prominent brow bones,

108
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,630
always standing with
his hands behind his back.

109
00:08:50,630 --> 00:08:52,200
He looked distinguished,

110
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:54,840
likely from an official or noble family.

111
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:57,550
And he spent quite generously.

112
00:09:04,550 --> 00:09:06,150
I brought a portrait artist.

113
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:07,910
You describe,

114
00:09:08,550 --> 00:09:09,480
and he'll draw.

115
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,630
Let me see

116
00:09:12,750 --> 00:09:14,630
who exactly

117
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:18,240
dares to steal my woman.
